{"tid":2250050,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–點解瘦削運動員都能夠跑畢馬拉松全程？（2）","createTime":"2020-10-19T22:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T08:33:49.000Z","uid":38861,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c9d0a2fac76739101624a3d82d383f3d3de764","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T22:45:04.000Z","msg":"上一篇用字錯誤，造成混亂，非常抱歉。今篇特設釐清因為用字錯誤所做成的概念困擾和錯誤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9NqvgW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9NqvgW.jpg&h=943da6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一篇提及身體消耗的卡路里是與步行總距離有關，其正確用字應為跑步總距離，非步行總距離。<br />\n<br />\n最終所得出的公式應為每1kg跑步1km就會消耗1卡路里，而非每1kg步行1km就會消耗1卡路里。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）之於公式為每1kg跑步1km就會消耗1卡路里，究竟是如何得出來的呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWarZas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWarZas.png&h=d078061d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是根據跑者真實實驗數據所得，跑速越快的話，能量消耗亦會越大，而且兩者的關係亦成直線相關趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n如果我們將Y-axis的單位同X-axis的單位相除，就可以推算出一個kcal/kg/km的常數(constant)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）上一篇因錯誤用字的關係，做成了假設體重一樣，跑步1km與行路1km消耗的卡路里均會一樣的假象，這裡特別在這方面略微深入講解一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRa31oS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRa31oS.png&h=76a7d395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每1kg每1km就會消耗1卡路里，只適用於跑步之上。<br />\n<br />\n從左面的圖中得知，當步速高過10km/hr的時候，能量消耗與步速才會成直線相關趨勢，每1kg每1km就會消耗1卡路里才可套用。<br />\n<br />\n而步速低過10km/hr的時候，能量消耗與步速再也不成直線相關趨勢，每1kg每1km就會消耗1卡路里的定律亦唔能夠得以套用。<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港人節奏急速，但以10km/hr的速度「行路」就應該不會太可行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）究竟身體能夠提供得到幾多卡路里予運動上?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsUMeJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsUMeJX.png&h=18b7bf39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖中所見，駭眼數字好足夠應付馬拉松的卡路里消耗，那麼為何這麼多人中途會無法支持下去呢?<br />\n<br />\n好大部份的原因，均歸咎於名為HIT THE WALL的現象，下篇再續。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=fb68a3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=bf6ce2ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=5d27ac82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://journals.physiology.org/doi/abs/10.1152/jappl.1963.18.2.367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.physiology.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1152%2Fjappl.1963.18.2.367&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=8d4cde03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://journals.physiology.org/doi/abs/10.1152/jappl.1963.18.2.367</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1859586/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC1859586%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=0156375a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1859586/</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-0251-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs42255-020-0251-4&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=d995d777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-0251-4</a>"},{"pid":"557bb5d999c28f5670fedcb2cfacf2dd7e76c1a1","tid":2250050,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T22:48:30.000Z","msg":"跑步怕猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3c79a931e049d79c9c69bd0bf2a9d42e9676b2","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"557bb5d999c28f5670fedcb2cfacf2dd7e76c1a1","tid":2250050,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T22:48:30.000Z","msg":"跑步怕猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從急步行著手？"},{"pid":"9e307559eb580296196a5ded2546c69272b7c3f4","tid":2250050,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T23:02:17.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"d2131867231987a658c32de21fe1d81d79b01c60","tid":2250050,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d4322ef148ffaa501b6b5c36c983b8f772f796","tid":2250050,"uid":34881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c964e7a21bd246d079bd4468d90ec5e371c62e","tid":2250050,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"香港人行步路都咁快，消耗脂肪率都高啲"},{"pid":"3bf4cf8bcec8e386591dfc69474485cdb68e424c","tid":2250050,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"巴打你開埋patreon好無多個channel睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4e1947b1746c2d4dce61e24979a0ab346633e4","tid":2250050,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"係咪瘦削既人都可以馬拉松式瘋狂做愛"},{"pid":"e40eaa11cbb51eaeafc759efaff18e196006c787","tid":2250050,"uid":100045,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"想請教下高手，我現時每星期跑一次步，每次8.5-10km<br />\n<br />\n近依幾次跑，跑到6-7km時，右腳膝頭哥後面個條筋有痛覺，愈跑愈扯住扯住..想問係受傷還是抽筋？ 跑完之後個個位都會痛一日，之後又無事"},{"pid":"6a87d993be6236dfab083da9ae8457fa03359ba0","tid":2250050,"uid":154421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"你不如諗清楚想講咩<br />\n連埋個標題改啦,原全唔知你想探討啲咩<br />\n不嬲跑長跑果啲都係瘦<br />\n你內文就話長時間運動要消耗脂肪黎提供能量<br />\n所以你標題就問點解瘦,小啲脂肪,小啲能量可以提供<br />\n都跑得完,但轉個頭拎個極端例子話2%其實都夠跑4次<br />\n自己打自己臉,原全黑人問號<br />\n咁到底你想討論乜?"},{"pid":"b2b3834fff7b17e967bc7b57480fd438e078a70a","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a87d993be6236dfab083da9ae8457fa03359ba0","tid":2250050,"uid":154421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"你不如諗清楚想講咩<br />\n連埋個標題改啦,原全唔知你想探討啲咩<br />\n不嬲跑長跑果啲都係瘦<br />\n你內文就話長時間運動要消耗脂肪黎提供能量<br />\n所以你標題就問點解瘦,小啲脂肪,小啲能量可以提供<br />\n都跑得完,但轉個頭拎個極端例子話2%其實都夠跑4次<br />\n自己打自己臉,原全黑人問號<br />\n咁到底你想討論乜?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣自己打自己嘴巴法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講本身就算極瘦的人，脂肪儲存量帳面上好足夠應付馬拉松所需的能量，然後再帶出HIT THE WALL的潛在問題，講解運動員可以捱得過的原因。"},{"pid":"cec7721080b78142a2a8c72b716fa048637115b8","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bf4cf8bcec8e386591dfc69474485cdb68e424c","tid":2250050,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"巴打你開埋patreon好無多個channel睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家連登、IG、Penana同步連載的模式已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2567b86a07ec79262962c4ab5b159698a365cb","tid":2250050,"uid":154421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2b3834fff7b17e967bc7b57480fd438e078a70a","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a87d993be6236dfab083da9ae8457fa03359ba0","tid":2250050,"uid":154421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"你不如諗清楚想講咩<br />\n連埋個標題改啦,原全唔知你想探討啲咩<br />\n不嬲跑長跑果啲都係瘦<br />\n你內文就話長時間運動要消耗脂肪黎提供能量<br />\n所以你標題就問點解瘦,小啲脂肪,小啲能量可以提供<br />\n都跑得完,但轉個頭拎個極端例子話2%其實都夠跑4次<br />\n自己打自己臉,原全黑人問號<br />\n咁到底你想討論乜?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣自己打自己嘴巴法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講本身就算極瘦的人，脂肪儲存量帳面上好足夠應付馬拉松所需的能量，然後再帶出HIT THE WALL的潛在問題，講解運動員可以捱得過的原因。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"但你個標題係點解瘦削都可以跑完全程喎<br />\n跟住下文自己話其實瘦，小脂肪都夠跑4次<br />\n咁你到底想問乜？<br />\n但其實你係想講咁小脂肪都夠跑四次<br />\n咁點解其他人跑唔完，因為理論上佢地仲多能量"},{"pid":"a774b112b580e3117bb0c438d64901b91dd015c1","tid":2250050,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb2567b86a07ec79262962c4ab5b159698a365cb","tid":2250050,"uid":154